scene.message:
Maki: Are you done with your{nl}
business? Let's hurry and{nl}
get out of here!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Wounds of the heart,{nl}
being invisible, are harder{nl}
to heal, it seems.{waitkey}{clearbox}No, no particular meaning.{nl}
It just crossed my mind{nl}
just now.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: What are you lazing{nl}
around for? Once we're healed,{nl}
we move out!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I want to vanquish the{nl}
Demons and restore the{nl}
peaceful town, but I feel a{nl}
little wistful too.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: When's the day gonna{nl}
come that I'm the idol of the{nl}
whole town — no, all of{nl}
Japan~!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ayase wants to go back{nl}
to being a normal high{nl}
school girl, and fast~!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: I'd like to get this{nl}
all settled soon.{waitkey}{clearbox}You've got someone waiting{nl}
for you to come home too,{nl}
haven't you?{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: It's dangerous, so you{nl}
mustn't go wandering around{nl}
too much!{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: I do hope the demons{nl}
vanish soon...{waitkey}{clearbox}Though if they do, it'll be{nl}
bad for my business. Ha ha ha.{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Now then, what'll{nl}
it be?{nl}
{ctl0e:17}{ret}

Doctor: It'll cost 1500 yen.{nl}
Is that all right?{waitkey}{nl}
{nl}

Doctor: A shame, but I can't{nl}
treat you with no money...{nl}
Come back with the fee.{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Skimp on treatment{nl}
now, and I hope it won't{nl}
come back to bite you.{waitkey}{ret}
